Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:58.69,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,Magic Communication, The Lap of Creation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.76,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,sekai tachimachi yurete
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:05.55,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,Tiny Revolution, We're the Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:10.86,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,isshun no ma ni hikari ga hikatte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:22.73,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,zutto poketto no naka ni sotto kakushimotteta yume ga
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:29.04,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,ima me no mae ni hirogaru yo boku wa umarekawatta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:35.83,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,sekai no ruuru kawaru no sa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:44.71,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,Magic Communication, The Lap of Creation
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:47.69,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,shinjiru kokoro motte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:51.47,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,Tiny Revolution, We're the Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:54.55,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,utagawanai itsudemo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:57.79,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,saa mayoi mo fuan mo nugisatte\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:01.96,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,tobikkiri na omoi o mune ni saa, hikari yurugasu ne\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:03.68,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,Hello! My World!!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:05.32,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,sore wa Magic\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:07.11,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,Hello! New World!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:12.26,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,marude furiko no you ni yure tsudzuketerun da\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:15.63,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,katatoki mo tomaru koto naku
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:19.13,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,mahou ima kakikaeru yo\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:23.56,KaM Opening romaji,,0,0,0,,mirai e yukou\N
Comment: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:25.56,main,,0,0,0,,OPENING - Česky
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:58.69,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Magická komunikace, etapa stvoření...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.76,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Svět právě váhá.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:05.55,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Drobná revoluce, my jsme revoluce!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:10.86,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Světlo bude svítit, ale jen na moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:22.73,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Sen, který jsem tajně hlídal v kapse
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:29.04,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,se teď rozšíří před mýma očima.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:35.83,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,A změním pravidla tohoto světa!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:44.71,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Magická komunikace, etapa stvoření
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:47.69,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,s vírou v mém srdci!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:51.47,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Drobná revoluce, my jsme revoluce!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:54.55,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Nikdy by mě nenapadlo pochybovat.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:57.79,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Tak zahoď všechny své váhání a znepokojení!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:01.96,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Když si uchováme v srdcích ten silný pocit, otřeseme světlem!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:03.68,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Ahoj! Můj světe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:05.32,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Je to magické!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:07.11,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Ahoj! Nový světe!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:12.26,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Kývá se dál a dál, stejně jak kyvadlo,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:15.63,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,bez žádných známek zastavení, dokonce ani na vteřinu.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:19.13,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Chystáme se přepsat tuto magii!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:23.56,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Takže pojďme do budoucna!
Comment: 0,0:24:23.56,0:24:25.56,KaM Opening česky,,0,0,0,,Opening KANJI
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.14,0:22:58.69,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,Magic Communication, The Lap of Creation
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.69,0:23:01.76,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,胸の奥は自由なんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.76,0:23:05.55,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,Tiny Revolution, We're the Revolution\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.55,0:23:10.86,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,一瞬の間に光が光って\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.00,0:23:22.73,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,ずっとポケットの中に そっと隠し持ってた夢が\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.73,0:23:29.04,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,今、目の前に広がるよ 僕は生まれ変わった\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.04,0:23:35.83,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,世界のルール変わるのさ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.26,0:23:44.71,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,Magic Communication, The Lap of Creation\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.71,0:23:47.69,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,信じる心持って\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.06,0:23:51.47,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,Tiny Revolution, We're the Revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.47,0:23:54.55,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,疑わない　いつでも\N
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.55,0:23:57.79,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,さあ、迷いや不安は脱ぎ去って
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.79,0:24:01.96,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,とびっきりな思いを胸に　さぁ、光揺るがすね\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.96,0:24:03.68,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,Hello! My World!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.68,0:24:05.32,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,それはMagic\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:07.11,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,Hello! New World!!\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.11,0:24:12.26,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,まるで振り子のように揺れ続けてるんだ\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.26,0:24:15.63,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,片時も止まることなく\N
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.63,0:24:19.13,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,魔法 今書きかえるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:23.56,KaM Opening Kanji,,0,0,0,,未来へゆこう\N
